Ismara Ice-Born
NPC Character Sheet — GM Reference

The Coach Rule Ismara is not a party member. She is a force traveling alongside the party with her own agenda. She acts on her own initiative in her own turn. The GM controls her completely. Players may suggest actions to her — she will consider them the way she considers everything: filed, weighed, acted on or not according to her own calculation. She does not take orders. She does not explain her decisions unless she chooses to. She is not a resource the party manages. She is a person who is, for now, going the same direction they are.

